”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41s-deryck-whibley-has-been-hospitalised-with-pneumonia-3498859">Sum 41 的 Deryck Whibley 因肺炎住院治疗</a>。</p> ;
